WEBVTT

00:10:29.892 --> 00:10:31.873
and high moral values.

00:10:32.436 --> 00:10:35.346
When asked about her driving
principles in life,

00:10:35.370 --> 00:10:36.801
she would respond,

00:10:36.825 --> 00:10:40.113
"I see inequity wherever it exists.

00:10:40.137 --> 00:10:43.029
I'm not afraid to call it by name,

00:10:43.053 --> 00:10:45.223
and I work hard to eliminate it.

00:10:45.659 --> 00:10:48.507
I vow to create a better earth."

00:10:49.870 --> 00:10:54.492
Shalon put those words into action
every day of her life.

